&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and dedicated chaplain to join our ecumenical team for three days each week, to be based at the Sutton site of the Royal Marsden NHS Foundation Trust. This is a wonderful opportunity to deliver pastoral and spiritual care in the context of a world-class cancer centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alistair McCulloch, Lead Chaplain, alistair.mcculloch@rmh.nhs.uk, 2818&lt;/p&gt;
